name: Pilgrimage to The Sea 2: Cast The First Stone Show
description:
Spectators who are dissapointed by “He that is without sin among you, let him first cast a stone at them” make a show. They encourage anyone to cast the first stone to sinners they bring to the show. The stone can shape in any kind of words, tweet, prayers, fire, etc. They won’t stop until they all are judged.
